#ident	"@(#)ihvkit:pdi/hba.guidelines/README	1.2"

This directory contains a set of guidelines that are mandatory reading for
every vendor who plans to develop, test, and support storage device drivers.

gen.guidelines:  Provides a set of general purpose guidelines for developing
		 UnixWare compatible device drivers.

tech.guidelines: A set of DOs/DON'Ts based on information gathered by a number
		 of in-house technical experts that should be extremely 
		 valuable for device driver programmers.
